🟢 STEP 2: MODEL TRAINING (train.py)

👉 Process:

Load dataset
Clean text
Feature extraction
Convert text → numbers (TF-IDF)
Train models
Models:
Classifier → predicts clarity
Regressor → predicts score
Output → models/*.pkl
🟢 STEP 3: SAVE MODELS

Models saved as:

models/clf_model.pkl
models/reg_model.pkl
models/vectorizer.pkl
models/le_clarity.pkl

